
// This Hyperlambda code dynamically converts the value of a node referenced by [.dp] to a type specified in the [.arguments] node of an action. The [convert] slot uses the [type] slot to determine the target type from the action's arguments, allowing for flexible type conversion based on the context of the action being executed.
convert:x:@.dp/#
   type:x:@.action/*/.arguments/*/{@get-name}/*/type
